Text: BIDEN: What is was, it was a tragedy, Martha.

Name: Joseph(Joe) R. Biden

Speech: We lost three other brave Americans.

Name: Joseph(Joe) R. Biden

Text: I can make absolutely two commitments to you and all the American people tonight.
Speech: I can make absolutely two commitments to you and all the American people tonight.

Name: Joseph(Joe) R. Biden

Text: One, we will find and bring to justice the men who did this.
Speech: One, we will find and bring to justice the men who did this.

Name: Joseph(Joe) R. Biden

Text: And secondly, we will get to the bottom of it, and whatever -- wherever the facts lead us, wherever they lead us, we will make clear to the American public, because whatever mistakes were made will not be made again.

Name: Joseph(Joe) R. Biden
